flood-doctor-website.name: Flood Doctor Website
flood-doctor-website.description: Modern React website for Flood Doctor water damage restoration company. Built with React, Vite, Tailwind CSS.
flood-doctor-website.instructions:
Build a comprehensive website for Flood Doctor, a water damage restoration company. The site should include:

- Homepage with hero section and service overview
- Service pages (water damage, mold remediation, storm damage, etc.)
- About page with company story and team
- Contact page with form and location info
- Blog section for SEO content
- Mobile-responsive design
- Core Web Vitals optimized
- Local SEO optimized for service areas

Tech Stack: React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, Node.js backend
Design: Use Google Blue #1a73e8 for CTAs, rounded-lg max corners, text-sm body text
